SAUCE: (TOMATO PUREE, TOMATOES, CORN OIL, SALT, OLIVE OIL, PEPPER, SPICES AND GARLIC). CANADIAN STYLE BACON (CHUNKED AND FORMED, INCLUDES PORK SIRLOIN HIPS. (CURED WITH WATER, SALT, POTASSIUM LACTATE, SUGAR, SODIUM NITRITE). PEPPERONI: (PORK AND BEEF, SALT, SPICES, DEXTROSE, LACTIC ACID STARTER CULTURE, OLEORESIN OF PAPRIKA, FLAVORINGS, SODIUM ASCORBATE, SODIUM NITRITE, B.H.A., B.H.T., CITRIC ACID). GRATED CHEESE: (ROMANO. PARMESAN, PART SKIM CHEESE MADE FROM: COW'S MILK, CHEESE CULTURE, SALT AND ENZYMES).
